  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">single-use</span> device for locating a deep-space <span class=\"name name-special\">Gaseous Sentience</span>. The lure generates an electromagnetic field of an intriguing nature to these highly advanced lifeforms.<br><br>Select the Lure and use Generate Field (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to begin the location process.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于定位深空<span class=\"name name-special\">气态智慧生命</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">一次性</span>装置。诱饵能够生成对这些高度进化生命体十分有吸引力的电磁场。<br><br>选择诱饵并使用生成力场（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）开始定位。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-stellar\">單次使用</span>的裝置，用來尋找深空中的<span class=\"name name-special\">氣體智慧生物</span>。誘餌會產生一個對高度先進的生命體倍具吸引力的電磁力場。<br><br>選擇誘餌並使用產生力場 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) 開始尋找地點。"
  },
